This SQL query calculates the percentage difference of student badges given during 2010 and 2011. It first counts the number of student badges given in each year using conditional counting, then calculates the percentage difference by subtracting the count from 2010 from the count from 2011, and dividing the result by the count from 2010. The result is then multiplied by 100 to get the percentage difference.
